{"tid":721051,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[溫故知新] [走線] 1998年老虎杯 最後一輪分組賽 印尼隊長烏龍球絕殺印尼","createTime":"2018-06-28T12:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T03:04:42.000Z","uid":120393,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"168d7b7df76abb9c2244a7b2a3b32a35b8124fe5","tid":721051,"uid":120393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"1998年老虎杯上，印尼和泰國在比賽中上演了令兩國足球蒙羞的鬧劇，兩支球隊都不願意在那場比賽中獲勝，這樣他們就可以避免在四強中和越南隊相遇。在那場比賽最後時刻，印尼隊隊長埃芬迪居然有意自入家門一球，這樣使得泰國隊3-2獲得了那場比賽的勝利，亞洲足聯賽後給予埃芬迪終生禁賽的處罰，並對印尼隊罰款4萬美元，禁止參加98年的亞運會。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DYegvcpVOyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDYegvcpVOyM&d=7euVI9lNcrrryKnQ5M9xm%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=76233f91\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DYegvcpVOyM</a><br />\n<br />\n白衫印尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef371da6ab007650a3c1fde69767c6f6b4c40ed3","tid":721051,"uid":120393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571e70bbce354a30a39b26c6e92c9181d27de564","tid":721051,"uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"痴線，咁撚明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b2ae00364ffe631964bf6a25c14d061e2be140","tid":721051,"uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"係啲濕鳩盃都要玩走線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26206b14089572e8705efc116fe1e5564bb7ac1","tid":721051,"uid":120393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"571e70bbce354a30a39b26c6e92c9181d27de564","tid":721051,"uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T12:13:45.000Z","msg":"痴線，咁撚明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 